    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this first-person survival horror adventure, we will play the role of young <strong>John</strong>, who drives late at night to visit his family after having been away for a long time. A mysterious entity forces him to enter the remains of Zoar, an uninhabited town that has been victim of an unknown evil that we will face with the help of strange objects. <strong>Sinister Soul</strong> brings a combat experience that will need your agility and coordination to confront the diverse enemies that you will encounter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2298740/extras/85b991a7a95999e6a96aa19d060861c2.avif?t=1764677433\" width=462 height=174 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2298740/extras/6662abfe6270508040b3196fee2d67f7.avif?t=1764677433\" width=800 height=374 /></span></p>",
